      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects a history of fastidious care. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to meet the highest standards of excellence. For the discerning driver who demands perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly distinguished motorcar.",
