    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It is in incredible shape and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs perfectly. It\u2019s such a smooth, reliable ride, and I\u2019m really going to miss it. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s been loved and well-cared for, this is the one! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
