      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with an uncompromising commitment to preservation, resulting in a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. The interior remains pristine, free of any signs of wear, while the exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster. For the discerning individual seeking an investment-grade asset, this vehicle offers an unparalleled acquisition opportunity. This is, without reservation, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
